msgstr ""

#: ../../source/cataloging.rst:1277 ../../source/cataloging.rst:1335
msgid "See Authorized headings sheet and AACR2. The first indicator should generally be a '1', to indicate that the entry is surname first. If the name consists only of a forename, however, the first indicator should be '0'."
