#: ../../source/cataloging.rst:1291
msgid "Put the location of publication in subfield 'a', the publisher in subfield 'b', and the year (or probable year) in subfield 'c'. See ISBD punctuation sheet.  The label is set dynamically from the second indicator so generally this would be set to '1' for Publisher: ."
